aptisDlcmiTable.name: aptisDlcmiTable
aptisDlcmiTable.reference: Draft American National Standard T1.617-1991, Annex D
aptisDlcmiTable.description: The Parameters for the Data Link Connection Management Interface corresponding to any given ifEntry. These parameters are logical extensions to those in object frDlcmiTable.

aptisDlcmiEntry.name: aptisDlcmiEntry
aptisDlcmiEntry.description: The Parameters for the Data Link Connection Management Interface.

aptisDlcmiIfIndex.name: aptisDlcmiIfIndex
aptisDlcmiIfIndex.description: The ifIndex value of the corresponding ifEntry.

aptisDlcmiXmtFramesDropped.name: aptisDlcmiXmtFramesDropped
aptisDlcmiXmtFramesDropped.description: The number of Tranmsitted frames dropped on this interface.

aptisDlcmiXmtOctetsDropped.name: aptisDlcmiXmtOctetsDropped
aptisDlcmiXmtOctetsDropped.description: The number of Tranmsitted octets dropped on this interface.

aptisDlcmiRcvFramesDropped.name: aptisDlcmiRcvFramesDropped
aptisDlcmiRcvFramesDropped.description: The number of Received frames dropped on this interface.

aptisDlcmiRcvOctetsDropped.name: aptisDlcmiRcvOctetsDropped
aptisDlcmiRcvOctetsDropped.description: The number of Received octets dropped on this interface.

aptisDlcmiRcvInvFrames.name: aptisDlcmiRcvInvFrames
aptisDlcmiRcvInvFrames.description: The number of invalid frames received on this interface.

aptisDlcmiRcvShortFrames.name: aptisDlcmiRcvShortFrames
aptisDlcmiRcvShortFrames.description: The number of frames containing less than 5 octets received on this interface.

aptisDlcmiRcvLongFrames.name: aptisDlcmiRcvLongFrames
aptisDlcmiRcvLongFrames.description: The number of frames containing greater than 8193 octets received on this interface.

aptisDlcmiRcvInvalidDLCI.name: aptisDlcmiRcvInvalidDLCI
aptisDlcmiRcvInvalidDLCI.description: The number of frames with an invalid DLCI received on this interface.

aptisDlcmiRcvUnknownDLCI.name: aptisDlcmiRcvUnknownDLCI
aptisDlcmiRcvUnknownDLCI.description: The number of frames with an unknown DLCI received on this interface.

aptisDlcmiRcvUnknownErrs.name: aptisDlcmiRcvUnknownErrs
aptisDlcmiRcvUnknownErrs.description: The number of frames with other errors received on this interface.

aptisDlcmiLMIStatusEnquiries.name: aptisDlcmiLMIStatusEnquiries
aptisDlcmiLMIStatusEnquiries.description: The total number of LMI status enquiries sent by the DTE or received by the DCE on this interface.

aptisDlcmiLMIFullStatusEnquiries.name: aptisDlcmiLMIFullStatusEnquiries
aptisDlcmiLMIFullStatusEnquiries.description: The total number of LMI full status enquiries sent by the DTE or received by the DCE on this interface.

aptisDlcmiLMIStatusResponses.name: aptisDlcmiLMIStatusResponses
aptisDlcmiLMIStatusResponses.description: The total number of LMI status responses received by the DTE or sent by the DCE on this interface.

aptisDlcmiLMIFullStatusResponses.name: aptisDlcmiLMIFullStatusResponses
aptisDlcmiLMIFullStatusResponses.description: The total number of LMI full status responses received by the DTE or sent by the DCE on this interface.

aptisDlcmiLMIUpdates.name: aptisDlcmiLMIUpdates
aptisDlcmiLMIUpdates.description: The total number of LMI status updates received by the DTE or sent by the DCE on this interface.

aptisDlcmiUnknownLMIMessagesRcvd.name: aptisDlcmiUnknownLMIMessagesRcvd
aptisDlcmiUnknownLMIMessagesRcvd.description: The total number of unknown LMI messages received on this interface.

aptisDlcmiBadLMIMessagesRcvd.name: aptisDlcmiBadLMIMessagesRcvd
aptisDlcmiBadLMIMessagesRcvd.description: The total number of LMI messages received with unknown or missing required Information Elements.

aptisDlcmiLostLMISequences.name: aptisDlcmiLostLMISequences
aptisDlcmiLostLMISequences.description: The total number of times a loss of sequencing in received LMI messages was detected by the DTE on this interface.

aptisDlcmiMissingLMIResponses.name: aptisDlcmiMissingLMIResponses
aptisDlcmiMissingLMIResponses.description: The total number of times a timeout occurred without receiving a response to an LMI request by the DTE on this interface.

aptisDlcmiUpTime.name: aptisDlcmiUpTime
aptisDlcmiUpTime.description: The duration that this data link has existed. This is the difference between the value of sysUpTime at the time of a 'get' and the value of sysUpTime at the time that the link level object was initialized.

aptisCircuitTable.name: aptisCircuitTable
aptisCircuitTable.description: A table containing information about specific Data Link Connection Identifiers and corresponding virtual circuits. These parameters are logical extensions to those in object frCircuitTable.

aptisCircuitEntry.name: aptisCircuitEntry
aptisCircuitEntry.description: The information regarding a single Data Link Connection Identifier.

aptisCircuitIfIndex.name: aptisCircuitIfIndex
aptisCircuitIfIndex.description: The ifIndex Value of the ifEntry this virtual circuit is layered onto.

aptisCircuitDlci.name: aptisCircuitDlci
aptisCircuitDlci.reference: Draft American National Standard T1.618-1991, Section 3.3.6
aptisCircuitDlci.description: The Data Link Connection Identifier for this virtual circuit.

aptisCircuitReceivedRBits.name: aptisCircuitReceivedRBits
aptisCircuitReceivedRBits.description: Number of times a status report for this circuit was received with the R-bit (congestion) set since the circuit was created.

aptisCircuitRateFallbacks.name: aptisCircuitRateFallbacks
aptisCircuitRateFallbacks.description: The number of times that the insertion rate was lowered (due to network congestion reports) since the circuit was created.

aptisCircuitRateFallforwards.name: aptisCircuitRateFallforwards
aptisCircuitRateFallforwards.description: The number of times that the insertion rate was lowered (due to lack of network congestion reports) since the circuit was created.

aptisCircuitFramesDroppedQueueFull.name: aptisCircuitFramesDroppedQueueFull
aptisCircuitFramesDroppedQueueFull.description: Number of frames which were dropped on this circuit because the hold queue was full.

aptisCircuitNormalSentOctets.name: aptisCircuitNormalSentOctets
aptisCircuitNormalSentOctets.description: Number of octets sent on this virtual circuit within the Commited Information Rate since the circuit was created.

aptisCircuitExcessSentOctets.name: aptisCircuitExcessSentOctets
aptisCircuitExcessSentOctets.description: Number of octets sent on this virtual circuit above the Commited Information Rate, but below the Excess Information Rate since the circuit was created.

aptisCircuitFramesQueuedBandwidth.name: aptisCircuitFramesQueuedBandwidth
aptisCircuitFramesQueuedBandwidth.description: Number of frames which were queued by the circuit in preference to exceeding the allowed burst rate on this circuit since the circuit was created.

aptisCircuitOctetsQueuedBandwidth.name: aptisCircuitOctetsQueuedBandwidth
aptisCircuitOctetsQueuedBandwidth.description: Number of octets placed on the hold queue since the circuit was created. Data is placed on the hold queue when the data would exceed the Excess Information Rate during a given time period.

aptisCircuitFramesOnQueue.name: aptisCircuitFramesOnQueue
aptisCircuitFramesOnQueue.description: Number of frames currently on the transmit hold queue.

aptisCircuitReceivedUnknownProtocol.name: aptisCircuitReceivedUnknownProtocol
aptisCircuitReceivedUnknownProtocol.description: Number of frames received and discarded due to unkown protocol ID.

aptisCircuitSentUnknownProtocol.name: aptisCircuitSentUnknownProtocol
aptisCircuitSentUnknownProtocol.description: Number of frames requested to be sent but were discarded due to an unknown protocol ID.

aptisCircuitReceivedUnknownFrame.name: aptisCircuitReceivedUnknownFrame
aptisCircuitReceivedUnknownFrame.description: Number of frames received and dropped due to an unknown frame type.

aptisCircuitReceivedUnknownOrg.name: aptisCircuitReceivedUnknownOrg
aptisCircuitReceivedUnknownOrg.description: Number of frames received and dropped due to an unknown organization unique identifier.

aptisCircuitNormalSentFrames.name: aptisCircuitNormalSentFrames
aptisCircuitNormalSentFrames.description: Number of frames sent on this virtual circuit within the Commited Information Rate since the circuit was created.

aptisCircuitExcessSentFrames.name: aptisCircuitExcessSentFrames
aptisCircuitExcessSentFrames.description: Number of frames sent on this virtual circuit above the Commited Information Rate, but below the Excess Information Rate since the circuit was created.

aptisCircuitOctetsDroppedQueueFull.name: aptisCircuitOctetsDroppedQueueFull
aptisCircuitOctetsDroppedQueueFull.description: Number of octets which were dropped on this circuit because the hold queue was full.
